text: Amanda Green (born 19 March 1984) is a New Zealand cricketer. She played in fourteen Women's One Day International cricket (WODI) matches and one Women's Twenty20 International cricket (WT20I) match between 2003 and 2004. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand women cricketers Category:New Zealand women One Day International cricketers Category:New Zealand women Twenty20 International cricketers Category:People from Waikato
